As Manager of Software Development I am responsible for leading a team of 14 software developers within the organization SDB Groep. I am accountable for managing and coordinating resources and processes to deliver software releases of SDB Groep products, while participating in defining the strategy for the product development team by driving initiatives that deliver on the SDB Groep vision.  

